         <section-title>Definition statement</section-title>
         <section-body><paragraph-text type="preamble">This place covers:</paragraph-text><paragraph-text type="body">Elevated transportation vehicles running on the upperside of the track.</paragraph-text><paragraph-text type="body">Following drawing shows one example for this group:</paragraph-text><paragraph-text type="body"><media id="media3.jpg" file-name="cpc-def-B61B-0003.jpg" type="jpeg" preferred-width="4.95cm" preferred-height="10.0cm"/></paragraph-text></section-body>
