<definition-item><classification-symbol scheme="cpc">B61B9/00</classification-symbol><definition-title>Tramway or funicular systems with rigid track and cable traction  (haulage clips <class-ref scheme="cpc">B61B12/12</class-ref>)</definition-title><definition-statement>
         <section-title>Definition statement</section-title>
         <section-body><paragraph-text type="preamble">This place covers:</paragraph-text><paragraph-text type="body">Transportation systems moving on a rigid track and being moved by a conveying cable or chain to which the transportation system can be coupled by means of clamping devices arranged thereon.</paragraph-text><paragraph-text type="body">Following drawing shows one example for this group:</paragraph-text><paragraph-text type="body"><media id="media5.png" file-name="cpc-def-B61B-0005.png" type="png" preferred-width="10.92cm" preferred-height="5.95cm"/></paragraph-text></section-body>
